questions.question:
Select all choices that are subspaces of R^2. Note: R denotes the set of real numbers.

A. {x in R^2 : x = [x_1, x_2]^T, alpha_1, alpha_2 in R, x = alpha_1 * [0, 1]^T + alpha_2 * [2, 1]^T}
B. {x in R^2 : x = [x_1, x_2]^T, alpha_1, alpha_2 in R, x = alpha_1 * [0, 1]^T + alpha_2 * [2, 1]^T + [1, 0]^T}
C. {x in R^2 : 5*x_1 + 4*x_2 = 0, 4*x_2 + 2*x_3 = 0}
D. {x in R^2 : 5*x_1 + 4*x_2 = 0, 4*x_2 + 2*x_3 = 4}

A. The span of two linearly independent vectors in R^2  B. The span shifted by [1,0]^T  C. Homogeneous linear system  D. Non-homogeneous linear system
